watchlist.overview: After being resurrected by a sinister entity, Art the Clown returns to Miles County where he must hunt down and destroy a teenage girl and her younger brother on Halloween night.  As the body count rises, the siblings fight to stay alive while uncovering the true nature of Art's evil intent.
watchlist.title: Terrifier 2

watchlist.overview: Two witches use a Ouija board to resurrect their friend after she dies in a tragic accident.
